Tokyo Port Shuts All 19 Water Gates After Quake Triggers Tsunami Warning

-- B y   K a n o k o   M a t s u y a m a
-- 
2011-03-11T06:25:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/tokyo-port-shuts-all-19-water-gates-after-quake-triggers-tsunami-warning.html
Tokyo port shut all 19 of its water
gates as it prepares for a tsunami, said Takashi Mifune,
spokesman for the Bureau of Port and Harbor of the Tokyo
Metropolitan Government. Japan’s Coast Guard is halting ships on
their way to entering Tokyo’s port, Mifune said in a phone
interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kanoko Matsuyama in Tokyo at 
 kmatsuyama2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
